      "comment": "CONTRADICTION (3) is a promising dog in the frame at 10 of 26 starts including nine wins and was in the minors again latest (25.62) over 450m at this track. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Has the ability and looks a key chance this line-up. MEPUNGA BROCKIE (8) flew the lids with a fast early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fifth (22.38) over 390m at this track. Has a solid record from this box including four wins and a minor placing. Can do much better this time. SURPRISE STAR (1) produced a moderate run last time when seventh at Ballarat over 450m behind Retaliation (25.98) in a Special conditions H. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Has ability and can atone. PAW VADA (4) is a last start winner who can measure up again.",
